snippet.title: Tale Of A Wolf - Progress Video
snippet.description:
Back in February I released the first prototype demo for Tale Of A Wolf, 8 months later I have released the Alpha demo!


Here is a short video showing the progress made so far!

Indie GoGo Campaign: http://tiny.cc/toawindiegogo
